{"tid":2327322,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳拜登擬與古巴逐步恢復建交，撤銷部份制裁措施","createTime":"2020-12-16T03:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T08:11:35.000Z","uid":38172,"like":7,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"dfbd47350eed88a805de922e6864a728743bdc07","tid":2327322,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T03:55:52.000Z","msg":"據彭博社引述知情人士透露，美國下屆總統拜登的團隊計劃逐漸與古巴恢復正常關係，並撤銷目前華府實施的制裁措施和規定。<br />\n 消息指拜登團隊的戰略包括放寬損害美國人和古巴人的旅行、投資和匯款限制，不過部分針對古巴侵犯人權的措施將繼續實施。<br />\n 華盛頓與哈瓦那的關係有望改善，不禁令人聯想起拜登在奧巴馬年代所倡導的古巴解凍政策。"},{"pid":"bffca2bed02ecc3ae4b9125ff1679df691ee7b3d","tid":2327322,"uid":2429,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T03:58:32.000Z","msg":"又幫垃圾共產狗國續命。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3a93850a46880a10679f01391d2cd398f37acc","tid":2327322,"uid":8308,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T03:58:56.000Z","msg":"好快就撤銷對中國制裁<br />\n中國同美國係各省/州均互設大使館 <br />\n孔子學院繼續係美國開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21e59a99d5d99d295db33a99af253dd5fcf6a0c","tid":2327322,"uid":29188,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae3a93850a46880a10679f01391d2cd398f37acc","tid":2327322,"uid":8308,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T03:58:56.000Z","msg":"好快就撤銷對中國制裁<br />\n中國同美國係各省/州均互設大使館 <br />\n孔子學院繼續係美國開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:00:13.000Z","msg":"有機可乘了，甴大大要趁機武統台灣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc873a4a8753657db95cc160326706908502eaa0","tid":2327322,"uid":55089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:05:10.000Z","msg":"左膠表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/